1. Moj *obaveza* danas je da odem u banku. (My *obligation* today is to go to the bank.)
2. On je ispunio svoju *obavezu* prema društvu. (He fulfilled his *duty* towards the society.)
3. Imam veliku *obavezu* prema svojoj porodici. (I have a great *responsibility* towards my family.)
4. *Obaveza* plaćanja računa je nešto što moramo svi da uradimo. (The *obligation* of paying bills is something we all have to do.)
5. Njihova *obaveza* je da redovno izveštavaju javnost. (Their *obligation* is to regularly inform the public.)
6. Učenici imaju *obavezu* da redovno dolaze na časove. (Students have an *obligation* to regularly attend classes.)
7. Država ima *obavezu* da štiti prava svojih građana. (The state has an *obligation* to protect the rights of its citizens.)
8. Njegova *obaveza* je da se brine o svojim zaposlenima. (His *responsibility* is to take care of his employees.)
9. Poslodavci imaju *obavezu* da obezbede sigurno i zdravo radno okruženje. (Employers have an *obligation* to provide a safe and healthy work environment.)
10. *Obaveze* koje imam u toku dana često utiču na moje raspoloženje. (The *obligations* I have during the day often affect my mood.)